<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net">
  <diagram name="Página-1" id="v4w0xNLlb51hintJ34AH">
    <mxGraphModel dx="7310" dy="-4242" grid="0" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="827" pageHeight="1169" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml predict_grpc_python\ntitle Predict — gRPC + Python Backend\n\nskinparam sequenceMessageAlign center\nskinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true\nskinparam maxMessageSize 200\nskinparam ParticipantPadding 20\nskinparam BoxPadding 10\nskinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5\nskinparam roundcorner 5\nskinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #333333\nskinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #333333\nskinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #DAE8FC\nskinparam sequenceActorBorderColor #333333\nskinparam noteBorderColor #AAAAAA\nskinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFFFCC\n\nactor \&quot;Caller\&quot; as Caller\n\nbox \&quot;mlinference::client\&quot; #EAF4FB\n    participant \&quot;InferenceClient\&quot; as IC\n    participant \&quot;GrpcClientBackend\&quot; as GCB\nend box\n\nbox \&quot;Network / gRPC\&quot; #F5F5F5\n    participant \&quot;WorkerService::Stub\&quot; as Stub\nend box\n\nbox \&quot;mlinference::worker (server)\&quot; #EAF7EA\n    participant \&quot;WorkerServiceImpl\&quot; as WSI\n    participant \&quot;InferenceEngine\&quot; as IE\n    participant \&quot;PythonBackend\&quot; as PB\nend box\n\nbox \&quot;CPython Interpreter\&quot; #FFF8E7\n    participant \&quot;MiiaModel\\n(user .py)\&quot; as Model\nend box\n\n== Setup (já conectado) ==\n\nCaller -&gt; IC : predict(\\n  model_id : string,\\n  inputs : Object)\nactivate IC\n\nIC -&gt; GCB : predict(\\n  model_id : string,\\n  inputs : Object)\nactivate GCB\n\nGCB -&gt; GCB : to_proto_struct(inputs)\\n: google::protobuf::Struct\n\nGCB -&gt; Stub : stub_-&gt;Run(\\n  PredictRequest {\\n    model_id,\\n    inputs: Struct\\n  }\\n) : PredictResponse\nactivate Stub\n\n== gRPC boundary ==\n\nStub -&gt; WSI : Predict(\\n  ServerContext*,\\n  PredictRequest*,\\n  PredictResponse*\\n) : grpc::Status\nactivate WSI\n\nWSI -&gt; WSI : from_proto_struct(\\n  request-&gt;inputs()\\n) : client::Object\n\nWSI -&gt; IE : predict(\\n  model_id : string,\\n  inputs : client::Object\\n) : InferenceResult\nactivate IE\n\nIE -&gt; PB : predict(\\n  inputs : client::Object\\n) : InferenceResult\nactivate PB\n\nnote right of PB\n  GIL acquired:\n  PyGILState_Ensure()\nend note\n\nPB -&gt; PB : inputs_to_py_dict(\\n  inputs : client::Object\\n) : PyObject* (dict)\n\nnote right of PB\n  Para cada key/value em inputs:\n  value_to_py(val) converte\n  Value → PyObject* recursivo\n  (número, bool, string, list, dict)\nend note\n\nPB -&gt; PB : PyTuple_Pack(1, py_inputs)\\n: PyObject* args\n\nPB -&gt; Model : PyObject_CallObject(\\n  py_predict_method_,\\n  args\\n) : PyObject* result\nactivate Model\n\nnote right of Model\n  model.predict(inputs: dict)\n  → retorna dict[str, np.ndarray]\nend note\n\nModel --&gt; PB : PyObject*\\n(dict[str, np.ndarray])\ndeactivate Model\n\nPB -&gt; PB : py_dict_to_outputs(\\n  py_result : PyObject*,\\n  outputs : Object&amp;\\n) : bool\n\nnote right of PB\n  Para cada key no dict:\n  PyArray_FROMANY → float32\n  PyArray_SIZE → count\n  floats → client::Value/Array\nend note\n\nnote right of PB\n  GIL released:\n  PyGILState_Release()\nend note\n\nPB -&gt; PB : metrics_.record(\\n  time_ms, success=true)\nPB -&gt; PB : touch()\n\nPB --&gt; IE : InferenceResult {\\n  success: bool,\\n  outputs: client::Object,\\n  inference_time_ms: double\\n}\ndeactivate PB\n\nIE --&gt; WSI : InferenceResult\ndeactivate IE\n\nWSI -&gt; WSI : to_proto_struct(\\n  result.outputs\\n) : google::protobuf::Struct\n\nWSI --&gt; Stub : grpc::Status::OK\\n+ PredictResponse\ndeactivate WSI\n\n== gRPC boundary ==\n\nStub --&gt; GCB : PredictResponse\ndeactivate Stub\n\nGCB -&gt; GCB : from_proto_struct(\\n  resp.outputs()\\n) : client::Object\n\nGCB --&gt; IC : PredictionResult\ndeactivate GCB\n\nIC --&gt; Caller : PredictionResult\ndeactivate IC\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="OFugE89OlIWmUVSY5UGE-3">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="1969" width="1651" x="-1422" y="7709" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
